A PERFECT multi-space event venue in MiamI
Intimate and large private gatherings
MILA offers endless possibilities for any kind of private dining and special events. From intimate 11-guest party, to full buyouts, our dedicated event team can curate a unique private dining experience for you, in any our different spaces from MILA Restaurant, to MILA Lounge or MILA Omakase.
Please fill out the inquiry forms and someone will get in touch in the next 48 hours.
MILA RESTAURANT
MILA Virtual Tour
LOUNGE | OMAKASE
View our special events brochure:
view
Indoor Private Dining Rooms
Our indoor private dining rooms are crafted to captivate, each offering a distinctive and refined atmosphere. From the sophisticated main dining room with its sweeping panoramic views to the chic, intimate enclaves throughout the restaurant, every space provides a unique and elegant backdrop, setting the stage for a truly memorable event.
With capacities ranging from intimate gatherings to grand celebrations, our rooms are designed to suit any occasion. Personalized menus and a professional events team are provided as standard, ensuring your event unfolds seamlessly from start to finish.
Outdoor Event Spaces
Immerse your guests in the splendor of Miami Beach with our exquisite outdoor event spaces, perfect for creating unforgettable experiences. Our rooftop terrace, offers breathtaking skyline views and comfort in an open-air setting. Each space captures the essence of Miami, providing an idyllic backdrop for any occasion.
MILA LOUNGE
Inspired by African tribes and the primitive design style of the mother continent, MILA Lounge is a multi-sensory space offering a transporting, glamorous and elevated secluded nightlife experience.
The unique venue draws upon minimalistic natural materials and earthy tones combined with opulent warm glow lamps, textured prints and shades, and a dramatic lush foliage hanging from the ceiling.
MILA Omakase
A 10-seat enclosed room offering the most exclusive and authentic journey in the far East, magnified by the Mediterranean influences of 26 times Michelin Restaurant awarded Chef Micha
ë
l Michaelidis.
The intimate, ultra luxurious and transporting space features a massive overhanging cherry blossom tree, a Japanese craftsmanship-inspired wallpaper screen, a dramatic marble countertop, a 500-years old hinoki wood cutting board, and wall-mounted niches serving as Members’ chopstick display.
Types of Events Hosted at MILA
For social events, MILA shines as an exceptional choice. From glamorous birthday celebrations and engagement dinners to festive holiday parties and sophisticated cocktail receptions, our venue has hosted it all.
Our dedicated team is committed to crafting bespoke experiences tailored to your company, party, or group’s unique needs. Along with our exquisite food and beverage offerings, we can provide custom decor, branding opportunities, unique entertainment, and state-of-the-art technical equipment for presentations and speeches.
Private Buyouts at MILA
Private buyouts at MILA offer a unique experience for those seeking unparalleled exclusivity. A private buyout of MILA secures exclusive access to our entire restaurant and its facilities. You can custom-design the floor plan, menu, and décor to perfectly suit your event’s theme and objectives. This level of customization and exclusivity guarantees your guests an unforgettable experience that truly reflects your vision.
For more information and to book your private event, visit
our website
today.
